snippet: A British government report on Egypt's Muslim Brotherhood has been delayed as ministers and officials disagree over its findings, the Financial Times reported on Sunday, citing official sources....

headline.print_headline: UK Report Into Muslim Brotherhood Delayed: Financial Times
headline.main: UK Report Into Muslim Brotherhood Delayed: Financial Times

lead_paragraph: A British government report on Egypt's Muslim Brotherhood has been delayed as ministers and officials disagree over its findings, the Financial Times reported on Sunday, citing official sources.
